[20.94081, "o", "\r\n\r\nDDx plugin loaded. Available `/ddx:` slash commands:\r\n\r\n- `/ddx:code-review` — Thorough code review with security focus\r\n- `/ddx:create-workflow` — Create a new DDx workflow interactively\r\n- `/ddx:commit-hooks` — Design and implement git commit hooks\r\n- `/ddx:gitignore` — Evaluate and create a comprehensive .gitignore\r\n- `/ddx:docs` — Create and maintain project documentation\r\n- `/ddx:prd` — Create a Product Requirements Document\r\n- `/ddx:github-actions` — Design and implement GitHub Actions CI/CD\r\n- `/ddx:helix` — Test-first development workflow (HELIX)\r\n- `/ddx:helix-alignment-review` — Top-down reconciliation review of a HELIX project\r\n"]
